<PageLayout 
  title="Contact Us | TokenCalc AI" 
  description="Get in touch with the TokenCalc AI team. We'd love to hear your feedback, suggestions, or questions."
>
  <h1>Contact Us</h1>

  <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a question, found a bug, or want to suggest a new feature, feel free to reach out using any of the methods below.</p>

  <h2>GitHub</h2>
  <p>TokenCalc AI is an open-source project. The best way to report bugs, request features, or contribute is through our GitHub repository:</p>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/ThatKJ/tokencalc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/ThatKJ/tokencalc</a></p>

  <h2>Open an Issue</h2>
  <p>If you've found a pricing discrepancy, a calculation error, or a UI bug, please <a href="https://github.com/ThatKJ/tokencalc/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">open an issue on GitHub</a>. Include as much detail as possible so we can investigate and fix it quickly.</p>

  <h2>Feature Requests</h2>
  <p>Have an idea for a new feature or a model you'd like us to support? We're always looking to improve. Submit a feature request through our <a href="https://github.com/ThatKJ/tokencalc/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Issues</a> page and tag it as an enhancement.</p>

  <h2>General Inquiries</h2>
  <p>For general questions about the tool, partnerships, or anything else, feel free to reach out via GitHub Discussions or by opening an issue.</p>

  <p>Thank you for using TokenCalc AI. Your feedback helps us build a better tool for the entire developer community.</p>

</PageLayout>
